name: Marigold Offering
description:
An herbal imprint on the crypto space.
Organic cupro fabric imbued with homegrown marigold petals. 
Coevolution: A process by which plant + animal species interact with, listen & respond to each other. 
Sale of this artwork supports my Natural Dye Lab and regenerative textile research. Join the plant revolution.
